Package: bibnets
Title: Citation, Co-Citation, and Bibliometric Network Construction
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", , "saqr@saqr.me", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5881-3109")),
    person("Sonsoles", "López-Pernas", role = "aut",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9621-1392")))
Description: Constructs bibliometric networks from scholarly data. Supports
    co-authorship, keyword co-occurrence, co-citation, bibliographic
    coupling, and direct citation networks with multiple counting and
    normalisation methods. Reads Scopus, Web of Science, BibTeX, RIS,
    OpenAlex, Lens.org, and Dimensions exports. Includes tools for
    temporal analysis, backbone extraction, and export to common network
    formats. Methods described in López-Pernas, Saqr & Apiola (2023)
    <doi:10.1007/978-3-031-25336-2_5> and Apiola, Saqr & López-Pernas
    (2023) <doi:10.1007/978-3-031-25336-2_6>.
